{"tid":449714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X中國炒價初曝光  只有微微水位","createTime":"2017-10-27T12:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T13:03:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3f347b387d39341c0f4a0e26f28ae59262a6dd","tid":449714,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"正當中國 AOS 長開之際，成功可以在首日取機的中國果農，已急不及待將 iPhone X 放到淘寶旗下的閑魚放售，當然售價並非 AOS 的官方建議零售價，而是微微炒高，但價錢則與坊間盛傳的炒高 HK$10,000 相距甚造，如非自用，又不是首日取得 iPhone X，看來要自求多福了！<br />\n<br />\n淘寶旗下二手交易平台閑魚，剛剛便被發現有不少會員將成功於 11 月 3 日領取 iPhone X 的確認信出貼放售，雖然售價比原來定價略高，但炒升就絕對談不上，以 64GB 為例，普遍只是多加 500 人民幣，即開賣價由 8,888 - 11,000 人民幣（約 HK$10,424 - HK$12,899）不等；256GB 版開賣價則由 10,688 - 15,000 人民幣（約 HK$12,535 - HK$17,590）不等，比官方定價 8,388 人民幣（64GB）及 9,688  人民幣（256GB）略炒升最高 50% 左右，與香港一直聲稱的回收價有一定距離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1930000/1934401/27102017suet_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1930000%2F1934401%2F27102017suet_04_600.jpg&h=7f07cc68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e79e6cdadf34534490bfc9038c726cb7b9739d99","tid":449714,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每部穩賺5k"},{"pid":"880432a3d37ec2f42890d01245dfd42bed745610","tid":449714,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"好驚呀 快d cut單呀"},{"pid":"47caa9db977e7c97df0582b4b1522b84ec883c05","tid":449714,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:28:06.000Z","msg":"50%  = 微微水位?"},{"pid":"930b6b28011bc68e54736933be92e9b52ca3d6e3","tid":449714,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每部穩賺5k</blockquot